	<!-- message -->
	<p>Pick lists. Big time.<br />
<br />
Arching storylines for better AP gain or rewards. Do a collect and find out about a rescue. Do the rescue get a bonus and find out about a slaughter Do the slaughter and find out about the boss that wants you dead. Kill him first and get big bonus and item. <br />
<br />
The loots you get in the runs should be turned in for AP rewards. Make staying after the win to see what named are up worth something. <br />
<br />
Fix the damn chests. There should a reason to open them EVERYtime. <br />
<br />
AP reward bonuses for killing named.  Larger bonuses or garunteed reward of some type for Assinate missions and rescues. <br />
<br />
Make the no drop Loots from collects worth an AP point or two. So people care about looting. <br />
<br />
Slaughters should give bonuses for how fast you complete them. I mean you are on a rampage. It should feel like it. (Also would be a reward for the DPS gods. Maybe a point for every minute faster than 45 minutes or something. Not huge but something. <br />
<br />
Rescues should lead to quests. For bonus AP items or both. See arcing storylines. Some of these quests should requre All sorts of weird stuff with clues as to where to get them.<br />
<br />
Edit <br />
<br />
Adding something here. Make the arching storylines based upon an item like a note. Hand the note to A specific Camps adventure getter and get tailored adventure type. (x number of bosses up Assinates and such) That way they can be spread out some and feel like a true adventure.<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Just a few ideas rehased over and over again. They are not listening however.. (Sigh)<br />
<br />
Snoww Silverhammer Bashy Bear E marr</p>
	
	
	
	
