	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Some good ideas here and some that could reinvigorate enthusiasm for LDoN again.  As a very gimp level 65, its difficult to find people my level willing to do Normal LDoNs and I sure as hell dont have the HPs to survive a hard.  Perhaps the intermediate difficulty between Normal and Hard (as well as corresponding increase to mob xps) might revive that and get more out of BoT.<br />
<br />
For me, there is a MAJOR content gap between what I can and can't accomplish due to my gear.  I can usually find a camp group in BoT and hope for a lucky roll but mind numbingly camp-pulling or I can sit and go LFG for an hour or so trying to find a level 65 group in LDoN.<br />
<br />
People like grinding AAs out in BoT and might be willing to grind out in LDoN if the xps was comparable.<br />
<br />
-Pjrell</p>
	
	
	
	
	
